Title: Classifying Vortex Solutions to Gauge Theories

Authors: Nathan F. Lepora and T. W. B. Kibble

Comments: 26 Pages. Latex. To be published in Phys. Rev. D

Journal-ref: Phys.Rev. D59 (1999) 125019

We classify the spectrum, family structure and stability of Nielsen-Olesenvortices embedded in a larger gauge group when the vacuum manifold is relatedto a symmetric space.